# Creates the ceph configuration file
#
# == Parameters
# [*fsid*] The cluster's fsid.
#   Mandatory. Get one with `uuidgen -r`.
#
# [*auth_type*] Auth type.
#   Optional. undef or 'cephx'. Defaults to 'cephx'.
#
# == Dependencies
#
# none
#
